===Verb===
{{de-verb|jobbe|jobst|jobt|jobte|gejobt|??|jobbe!|jobt!|haben}}
„[[jobben]]“ means for adults to have: 
* many quickly varying jobs, or
* always only small engagements for work, or
* (a) part-time employment(s),
with low pay, and probably spend little efford on them.

For school children, students, etc. „[[jobben]]“ usually means to have a holliday job.